## Summary
This documentation page explains Amplitude's Lifecycle Chart, a tool that categorizes active users into new, current, and returning segments while also tracking dormant users, allowing product teams to visualize user base growth over time. The chart offers three views (Growth, Dormant, and Pulse) to analyze different aspects of user engagement patterns and product growth.

